SCHEMA: universe/time_model.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.universe.time_model
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic universe time-axis capabilities and constraints.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record time_model
  required:
    - time_model_id: id
    - single_tick_axis: bool
    - allow_variable_dt: bool
    - allow_branching: bool
    - allow_retroactive_mutation: bool
    - extensions: map
